com.xtructure.xutil.xml
Class XmlBinding

java.lang.Object
  javolution.xml.XMLBinding
      com.xtructure.xutil.xml.XmlBinding
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javolution.lang.Reusable, javolution.xml.XMLSerializable
public final class XmlBinding
extends javolution.xml.XMLBinding

An extension of XMLBinding which makes defining bindings for multiple class more convenient.

The constructor may be used to simply bind the given classes to their simple names. The XmlBinding.Builder class allows for specific binding definitions and merging of XmlBindings.

Author:
Luis Guimbarda
